729671f-a.title: Richmond: Simonson Avenue - Walker Street
729671f-a.text:
182 to 160 Simonson Avence, west side, north from Walker SStreet. At the time of this photograph Walker Street had not yet been cut through at this point. When cut through it would be about sixty feet this side of the first house.
April 23, 1932
P. L. Sperr
